    {
      "source_id": "claude-blog",
      "source_name": "Claude Blog",
      "category": "A",
      "title_zh": "Anthropic 經濟未來計畫（Economic Futures）",
      "url": "https://www.anthropic.com/economic-futures",
      "summary_zh": "Anthropic 推出「經濟未來計畫」，透過研究補助、政策論壇和經濟指數（Economic Index）追蹤 AI 對經濟的實際影響。該指數分析 Claude 在美國各州和數百種職業的使用情況，揭示 AI 採用的地理與產業分布不均現象，並探討對軟體開發等領域的影響。",
      "content_zh": "## Anthropic 經濟未來計畫\n\nAnthropic 推出「經濟未來計畫」（Economic Futures Program），旨在支持 AI 經濟影響的研究與政策制定。\n\n### 計畫核心\n- **研究補助**：資助相關學術與政策研究\n- **政策論壇**：提供討論平台，促進政策對話\n- **實證數據**：提供 AI 實際應用的證據\n\n## Anthropic 經濟指數（Economic Index）\n\n### 指數目標\n追蹤 AI 在美國與全球經濟中的角色，分析 Claude 在經濟各領域的使用情況。\n\n### 研究範圍\n- **地理分布**：涵蓋美國所有州的 AI 採用情況\n- **職業分析**：追蹤數百種職業如何使用 Claude\n- **企業應用**：研究企業級 AI 採用模式\n\n### 主要發現\n\n#### 最新研究（2026年1月）\n- **經濟基本單元**：建立理解 AI 使用的新分析框架\n- **經濟原語報告**：定義 AI 經濟影響的基礎概念\n\n#### 2025年研究成果\n- **地理與企業採用不均**（9月）：揭示 AI 採用在地理位置和企業規模上的顯著差異\n- **軟體開發影響**（4月）：分析 AI 對軟體開發工作流程的影響\n- **Claude 3.7 Sonnet 洞察**（3月）：從新版本使用數據獲得的見解\n\n#### 英國與歐洲擴展（11月）\n在英國和歐洲啟動經濟未來計畫，擴大研究範圍。\n\n### 隱私保護技術\n\n經濟指數採用 **Clio 系統**，這是一個創新的隱私保護分析框架，能在分析 Claude 對話數據的同時完全保護使用者隱私。\n\n### 政策影響\n\n**經濟未來研討會提案**：華盛頓特區研討會參與者提出的政策建議，為 AI 經濟政策制定提供實務參考。\n\n---\n\n此計畫代表 Anthropic 對 AI 社會影響的長期承諾，透過實證研究協助政策制定者、企業和研究者理解 AI 技術的經濟轉型效應。",
      "content_original": "Economic Futures\n\nThe Anthropic Economic Futures program aims to support research and policy development for addressing the economic impacts of AI. It provides research grants, forums for policy discussion, and evidence on real-world AI use. \n\nEconomic Index\n\nAnalyzing how Claude is used across the economy.\n\nThe Anthropic Economic Index reveals the shape of AI adoption across the world. Here, you can explore the data behind our research to understand how people are using Claude across every US state and hundreds of occupations.\n\nRead more\n\nLatest updates\n\nSearch\n\nDate\n\nCategory\n\nTitle\n\nJan 15, 2026\n\nEconomic Research\n\nAnthropic Economic Index: New building blocks for understanding AI use\n\nJan 15, 2026\n\nEconomic Research\n\nAnthropic Economic Index report: economic primitives\n\nNov 5, 2025\n\nEconomic Research\n\nLaunching the Anthropic Economic Futures Programme in the UK and Europe\n\nSep 15, 2025\n\nEconomic Research\n\nAnthropic Economic Index report: Uneven geographic and enterprise AI adoption\n\nSep 15, 2025\n\nEconomic Research\n\nAnthropic Economic Index: Tracking AI’s role in the US and global economy\n\nApr 28, 2025\n\nSocietal Impacts\n\nAnthropic Economic Index: AI’s impact on software development\n\nMar 27, 2025\n\nSocietal Impacts\n\nAnthropic Economic Index: Insights from Claude 3.7 Sonnet\n\nFeb 10, 2025\n\nSocietal Impacts\n\nThe Anthropic Economic Index\n\nAnnouncements\n\nEconomic Futures Symposium Proposals\n\nA selection of policy proposals from attendees at our DC Economic Futures Symposium\n\nRead more\n\nIntroducing Anthropic Economic Futures Program\n\nWe’re launching the Anthropic Economic Futures program, a multidisciplinary effort that builds upon our existing economic research efforts.\n\nRead more\n\nPreserving privacy\n\nThe Anthropic Economic Index is made possible by Clio, a system that allows us to analyze conversations with Claude while preserving user privacy.\n\nRead more",
      "content_html": "<section class=\"LandingPageSection-module-scss-module__ZSMdoa__root bg-default\" data-theme=\"ivory\"><div class=\"page-wrapper\"><div class=\"HeroTwoColumn-module-scss-module__pM-nba__root\"><div class=\"HeroTwoColumn-module-scss-module__pM-nba__titleSubhead\"><h1 class=\"headline-1\">Economic Futures</h1></div><div class=\"HeroTwoColumn-module-scss-module__pM-nba__bodyCtas\"><p class=\"body-1 serif\">The Anthropic Economic Futures program aims to support research and policy development for addressing the economic impacts of AI. It provides research grants, forums for policy discussion, and evidence on real-world AI use. </p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"LandingPageSection-module-scss-module__ZSMdoa__root bg-default LandingPageSection-module-scss-module__ZSMdoa__flushTop\" data-theme=\"ivory\"><div class=\"page-wrapper\"><div class=\"LandingPageSection-module-scss-module__ZSMdoa__borderTop\"></div></div><div class=\"page-wrapper\"><div class=\"FeaturedBlock-module-scss-module__3NR_tG__root\"><div class=\"FeaturedBlock-module-scss-module__3NR_tG__content\"><div class=\"FeaturedBlock-module-scss-module__3NR_tG__header\"><span class=\"caption bold\">Economic Index</span><h2 class=\"headline-4\">Analyzing how Claude is used across the economy.</h2></div><div class=\"FeaturedBlock-module-scss-module__3NR_tG__footer\"><p class=\"body-3 FeaturedBlock-module-scss-module__3NR_tG__body\">The Anthropic Economic Index reveals the shape of AI adoption across the world. Here, you can explore the data behind our research to understand how people are using Claude across every US state and hundreds of occupations.</p><div class=\"FeaturedBlock-module-scss-module__3NR_tG__ctaGroup\"><a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/economic-index\" class=\"Button-module-scss-module__f9ZZrG__button Button-module-scss-module__f9ZZrG__small Button-module-scss-module__f9ZZrG__tertiary Button-module-scss-module__f9ZZrG__iconRight\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"caption\">Read more</span><span class=\"Button-module-scss-module__f9ZZrG__icon\"><svg class=\"Icon-module-scss-module__lqbdHG__icon\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 21 21\"><path d=\"M4.14585 9.87492L14.4584 9.87492L9.60419 5.04158L10.5 4.14575L16.8542 10.4999L10.5 16.8541L9.60419 15.9583L14.4584 11.1249L4.14585 11.1249L4.14585 9.87492Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></span></a></div></div></div><div class=\"FeaturedBlock-module-scss-module__3NR_tG__media\"><figure class=\"FeaturedBlock-module-scss-module__3NR_tG__image\"><img alt=\"Analyzing how Claude is used across the economy.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-cdn.anthropic.com%2Fimages%2F4zrzovbb%2Fwebsite%2F1e2cc2ea6907317ec1daf171d8a8889c170fc727-1600x900.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-cdn.anthropic.com%2Fimages%2F4zrzovbb%2Fwebsite%2F1e2cc2ea6907317ec1daf171d8a8889c170fc727-1600x900.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://www.anthropic.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-cdn.anthropic.com%2Fimages%2F4zrzovbb%2Fwebsite%2F1e2cc2ea6907317ec1daf171d8a8889c170fc727-1600x900.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></figure></div></div></div></section><section class=\"LandingPageSection-module-scss-module__ZSMdoa__root bg-default LandingPageSection-module-scss-module__ZSMdoa__flushTop\" data-theme=\"ivory\"><div class=\"page-wrapper\"><div class=\"LandingPageSection-module-scss-module__ZSMdoa__borderTop\"></div></div><div class=\"page-wrapper\"><div class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__header\"><h2 class=\"headline-4\">Latest updates</h2><div class=\"SearchFilter-module-scss-module__d4ijlG__container\"><label for=\"search-input\" class=\"SearchFilter-module-scss-module__d4ijlG__srOnly\">Search</label><svg class=\"Icon-module-scss-module__lqbdHG__icon SearchFilter-module-scss-module__d4ijlG__icon\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\