 for understanding AI use</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/research/anthropic-economic-index-january-2026-report\" class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__listItem\"><div class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__meta\"><time class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__date body-3\">Jan 15, 2026</time><span class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__subject body-3\">Economic Research</span></div><span class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__title body-3\">Anthropic Economic Index report: economic primitives</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/research/estimating-productivity-gains\" class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__listItem\"><div class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__meta\"><time class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__date body-3\">Nov 25, 2025</time><span class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__subject body-3\">Economic Research</span></div><span class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__title body-3\">Estimating AI productivity gains from Claude conversations</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/research/anthropic-economic-index-september-2025-report\" class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__listItem\"><div class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__meta\"><time class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__date body-3\">Sep 15, 2025</time><span class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__subject body-3\">Economic Research</span></div><span class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__title body-3\">Anthropic Economic Index report: Uneven geographic and enterprise AI adoption</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/research/economic-index-geography\" class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__listItem\"><div class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__meta\"><time class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__date body-3\">Sep 15, 2025</time><span class=\"PublicationList-module-scss-module__KxYrHG__subject b