available in the U.S. for free-tier users.</li>\n<li>You control which apps connect and can turn connections on or off anytime.</li>\n</ul>\n          </p>\n          <small class=\"article-summary-modal__legal\">\n            Summaries were generated by Google AI. Generative AI is experimental.\n          </small>\n        </div>\n      \n\n      \n      <div class=\"article-sumary-modal__explore\">\n        <h4 class=\"article-summary-modal__explore-title\">\n          Explore other styles:\n        </h4>\n        <div class=\"article-summary-modal__explore-styles\">\n          <ul class=\"article-summary-modal__chips\">\n            \n            <li>\n              <button class=\"article-summary-modal__chip--btn\" aria-label=\"General summary\" data-summary-id=\"ai_summary_1\" aria-pressed=\"true\">\n                <span class=\"article-summary-modal__chip active\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  General summary\n                </span>\n              </button>\n            </li>\n            \n            <li>\n              <button class=\"article-summary-modal__chip--btn\" aria-label=\"Bullet points\" data-summary-id=\"ai_summary_2\" >\n                <span class=\"article-summary-modal__chip \" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  Bullet points\n                </span>\n              </button>\n            </li>\n            \n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n\n      <button class=\"article-summary-modal__icon\" title=\"Close summary\">\n        <svg\n  \n  class=\"h-c-icon h-c-icon__close\"\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  aria-hidden=\"true\"\n  \n  \n  \n  \n>\n  <use\n    xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"\n    href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20260310-1630#ai-modal-close\"></use>\n</svg>\n\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n      \n    \n    <div class=\"article-share__wrapper\"\n      data-analytics-module='{\n        \"module_name\": \"Hero Share\",\n        \"section_header\": \"Bri