gin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">DeepSeek-V3.2 是我们当前正式提供服务的模型，官网网页、APP、API 模型均已由 DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp 升级为正式版 DeepSeek-V3.2，使用方式不变。</span></span></p><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时，为了方便社区评测与研究，我们非正式部署了 DeepSeek-V3.2-Speciale 的 API 服务，API 用户可以通过设置</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">base_url=\"</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(77, 107, 254);\">https://api.deepseek.com/v3.2_speciale_expires_on_20251215</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\"</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">访问该模型。该模型 API 价格不变，只支持思考模式下的对话功能，不支持工具调用等功能，最大输出长度默认为 128K，支持时间截止至北京时间 2025-12-15 23:59。</span></span></p><section><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Q927dUoN9ouuKcxTc26chgGknEb&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;该模型 API 价格不变，只支持思考模式下的对话功能，不支持工具调用等功能，最大输出长度默认为 128K，支持时间截止至北京时间 2025-12-15 23:59。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+1g*1+1*0+t&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7238788719937880068&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7313741941510488068&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:2}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:false,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;0bc22312-de2a-4890-b869-716720e46b46&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:58,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:143,&quot;end&quot;:225},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;BbFidxd8Wo3cQjx93AKcG3mnntg&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></section><h2 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">思考模式下的工具调用</span></span></h2><section><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Q927dUoN9ouuKcxTc26chgGknEb&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;思考模式下的工具调用&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+a&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7238788719937880068&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading2&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;82535e00-96a7-48f1-92de-a9d40afbf942&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:57,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:10},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;Gfygd6DD8oQCh3xIpNQc7rq9n7g&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></section><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本次 API 更新</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">支持了 DeepSeek-V3.2 思考模式下的工具调用能力</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。当前在思考模式下，模型能够经过多轮的思考 + 工具调用，最终给出更详尽准确的回答。下图为思考模式下进行工具调用的 API 请求示意图：</span></span></p><section><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Q927dUoN9ouuKcxTc26chgGknEb&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;本次 API 更新支持了 DeepSeek-V3.2 思考模式下的工具调用能力。当前在思考模式下，模型能够经过多轮的思考 + 工具调用，最终给出更准确的回答。下图为思考模式下进行工具调用的 API 请求示意图：&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+9*0*1+u*0+1*2+2*0+q*2+2*0+z&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7110121313687126017&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;bold&quot;,&quot;true&quot;],&quot;2&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7313741941510488068&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:3}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;2327a6c8-c4ea-44ae-844a-96c512f45857&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:31,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:105},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;P8nodTGEoozbAmxTCnVchgXHnob&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></section><section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100002033\" data-ratio=\"0.5425925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/pkWC42uvwkmkWUpqHRFeNvCZJ4dbmZuohmETA6yqx5dMVzYKuheegKvoyth3YZnVdcbnXMNNTJ2WIm9FEpyXDw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\"></section><ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\"><li><p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在回答问题 1 过程中（请求 1.1 - 1.3），模型进行了多次思考 + 工具调用后给出答案。在这个过程中，用户需回传思维链内容（reasoning_content）给 API，以让模型继续思考。</span></span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在下一个用户问题开始时（请求 2.1），需删除之前的思维链，并保留其它内容发送给 API。</span></span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更详细的使用方法请参考 API 文档：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(77, 107, 254);\">https://api-docs.deepseek.com/zh-cn/guides/thinking_mode</span></span></p></li></ul><section><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Q927dUoN9ouuKcxTc26chgGknEb&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;https://api-docs.deepseek.com/zh-cn/guides/thinking_mode。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1*2+u*0*1+r&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7110121313687126017&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;comment-id-7577592450978483406&quot;,&quot;true&quot;],&quot;2&quot;:[&quot;link-id&quot;,&quot;1c7fc1f0-4a2d-4310-a8ac-8b18e0b10aca&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:3}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:false,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;8e0fbcec-78ce-4338-842d-c53d80380117&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:72,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:19,&quot;end&quot;:76},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;ZxK4dIULxofm3Xxf5fwcICXSnMX&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></section><section><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></section><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">DeepSeek-V3.2 的思考模式也</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">增加了对 Claude Code 的支持</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，用户可以通过将模型名改为 deepseek-reasoner，或在 Claude Code CLI 中按 Tab 键开启思考模式进行使用。但需要注意的是，思考模式</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">未充分适配 Cline、RooCode</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;等使用非标准工具调用的组件，我们建议用户在使用此类组件时继续使用</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">非思考</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模式。</span></span></p><section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !import