ta-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/feature/ai-agent-new-wave/39720-exclusive-interview-going-cloud-huang-how-to-evolve-from-ai-agents-to-ai-employee-management\" title=\"專訪 Going Cloud 黃柏淞：我們該怎麼從 AI Agent，走到「AI 員工管理術」？\">專訪 Going Cloud 黃柏淞：我們該怎麼從 AI Agent，走到「AI 員工管理術」？</a>\n                </h3>\n                                    <p class=\"post_description js-auto_break_text\">因應企業導入多個代理式 AI 後的組織管理挑戰，科科科技旗下 Going Cloud 推出多代理系統（MAS）服務。其核心在建立協作協定，將 AI 視為組織成員納入流程，以解決大型企業跨部門協作與調度的複雜性。</p>\n                                <ul class=\"post_meta\">\n                    <li class=\"post_date\">\n                        <span>2025/10/02</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        <span class=\"post_author\">\n                                                                                            <a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/author/chris\" title=\"Posts by Chris\" class=\"author url fn \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" rel=\"author\">Chris</a>\n                                                    </span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                                                                                <a class=\"hero_slide_tag \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/tag/1574-AWS\">AWS</a>\n                                                                                    、                                                        <a class=\"hero_slide_tag \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/tag/15217-KKCompany\">KKCompany</a>\n                                                                                    、                                                        <a class=\"hero_slide_tag \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/tag/26707-AI%20Agent\">AI Agent</a>\n                                                                                    、                                                        <a class=\"hero_slide_tag \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/tag/29478-Going%20Cloud\">Going Cloud</a>\n                                            </li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n            <div class=\"post_list_item \">\n\n                            <a class=\"post_category badge\" style=\"background-color: #ea5496\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/category/ai\">人工智慧</a>\n            \n            <a class=\"post_cover \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/feature/ai-agent-new-wave/39672-taboola-ai-agent\">\n                <div class=\"post_cover_inner\" style=\"background-image: url('https://bucket-image.inkmaginecms.com/version/list/9dde7c0f-a597-445c-80dd-9a93db8a4006/image/2025/09/b87fe4cf-4aa3-4842-963f-5bde36707765.jpg');\">\n                                    </div>\n            </a>\n            <div class=\"post_list_item_content\">\n                <h3 class=\"post_title\">\n                    <a class=\"js-auto_break_title \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/feature/ai-agent-new-wave/39672-taboola-ai-agent\" title=\"專訪 Taboola 俞寧寧：請用 AI Agent 面對 Google AI Overview 流量衝擊\">專訪 Taboola 俞寧寧：請用 AI Agent 面對 Google AI Overview 流量衝擊</a>\n                </h3>\n                                    <p class=\"post_description js-auto_break_text\">以 Google 的 AI Overview 為首，各式各樣的生成式 AI 正在激烈地重新塑造全球媒體格局，在這場劇變中媒體到底該怎麼面對？或許全球最大的成效廣告商 Taboola 會有答案。</p>\n                                <ul class=\"post_meta\">\n                    <li class=\"post_date\">\n                        <span>2025/09/25</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        <span class=\"post_author\">\n                                                                                            <a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/author/chris\" title=\"Posts by Chris\" class=\"author url fn \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" rel=\"author\">Chris</a>\n                                                    </span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                                                                                <a class=\"hero_slide_tag \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/tag/16389-Taboola\">Taboola</a>\n                                                                                    、                                                        <a class=\"hero_slide_tag \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/tag/29422-%E4%BF%9E%E5%AF%A7%E5%AF%A7\">俞寧寧</a>\n                                                                                    、                                                        <a class=\"hero_slide_tag \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/tag/29423-Google%20AI%20Overview\">Google AI Overview</a>\n                                            </li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n            <div class=\"post_list_item \">\n\n                            <a class=\"post_category badge\" style=\"background-color: #ea5496\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/category/startup\">新創</a>\n            \n            <a class=\"post_cover \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/feature/ai-agent-new-wave/39523-jtcg-raccoonai-zendesk-ai-agent\">\n                <div class=\"post_cover_inner\" style=\"background-image: url('https://bucket-image.inkmaginecms.com/version/list/9dde7c0f-a597-445c-80dd-9a93db8a4006/image/2025/09/82d532b9-20d2-486e-8261-2fe309a3f17e.png');\">\n                                    </div>\n            </a>\n            <div class=\"post_list_item_content\">\n                <h3 class=\"post_title\">\n                    <a class=\"js-auto_break_title \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/feature/ai-agent-new-wave/39523-jtcg-raccoonai-zendesk-ai-agent\" title=\"專訪 RACCOON AI 周益鑫：獨闢「中間賽道」的新創，怎打造解決率 80% 的客服 AI Agent？\">專訪 RACCOON AI 周益鑫：獨闢「中間賽道」的新創，怎打造解決率 80% 的客服 AI Agent？</a>\n                </h3>\n                                    <p class=\"post_description js-auto_break_text\">詹姆斯科技創辦人周益鑫 於學生時代創業，之後投入代理 Zendesk，並發現亞洲市場 CRM 在地化需求。就在 ChatGPT 問世後，他打造出全新 RACCOON AI，強調人機協作賦能客服；產品以模型編排引擎、高階腳本及 AI 品管建立技術護城河。</p>\n                                <ul class=\"post_meta\">\n                    <li class=\"post_date\">\n                        <span>2025/09/09</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        <span class=\"post_author\">\n                                                                                            <a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/author/claire\" title=\"Posts by Claire\" class=\"author url fn \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" rel=\"author\">Claire</a>\n                                                    </span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                                                                                <a class=\"hero_slide_tag \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/tag/26707-AI%20Agent\">AI Agent</a>\n                                                                                    、                                                        <a class=\"hero_slide_tag \" data-gtm-category=\"\" data-gtm-label=\"\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/tag/29271-RACCOON%20AI\">RACCOON AI</a>\n                                            </li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <ul class=\"pagination\">\n        <li class=\"pagination_item-prev-wrapper\">\n                            <span class=\"pagination_item pagination_item-prev is-disable\">上一頁</span>\n                    </li>\n                                                                                                                    \n                            <li class=\"pagination-isCurrent-wrapper\">\n                    <span class=\"pagination_item is-current\">1</span>\n                </li>\n                                            \n                            <li>\n                    <a class=\"pagination_item\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/feature/ai-agent-new-wave?page=2\">2</a>\n                </li>\n                                            \n                            <li>\n                    <a class=\"pagination_item\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/feature/ai-agent-new-wave?page=3\">3</a>\n                </li>\n                                                                    <li class=\"pagination_item-next-wrapper\">\n                            <a class=\"pagination_item pagination_item-next\" href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/feature/ai-agent-new-wave?page=2\">下一頁</a>\n                    </li>\n    </ul>\n\n            <div class=\"subscribe_block\">\n    <div class=\"subscribe_block_title\">訂閱 INSIDE</div>\n    <div class=\"subscribe_block_description js-auto_break_text\">隨時關注最新創業、科技、網路、工作訊息。</div>\n    <div class=\"subscribe_block_action\">\n        <div class=\"subscribe_block_social_list\">\n            <a class=\"subscribe_block_social_item\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cyberbuzz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f\"></i></a>\n            <a class=\"subscribe_block_social_item\" href=\"https://twitter.com/insideCyberbuzz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"fab fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n            <a class=\"subscribe_block_social_item\" href=\"https://line.me/ti/p/@paq1370n\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"fab fa-line\"></i></a>\n            <a cl